description: Deletes identities from an identity pool. You can specify a list of 1-60 identities that you want to delete. You must use Amazon Web Services developer credentials to call this operation.

nested_items.name: UnprocessedIdentityIds
nested_items.description: An array of UnprocessedIdentityId objects, each of which contains an ErrorCode and IdentityId.

nested_items.name: IdentityId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier in the format REGION:GUID.

nested_items.name: ErrorCode
nested_items.description: The error code indicating the type of error that occurred.
